snippet.title: Best of Drama
snippet.description: Hello! Welcome to our new channel, Best of Drama. Where we will bring you all the new exciting videos on everything drama related! We upload twice a week so be on the look out for our new videos that you do not want to miss! Don't forget to subscribe to never miss out on a video! Also, leave suggestions on what you'd like to see next as that could be the next video. :)
